) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=36 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;INSERT INTO fc_cms VALUES("1","Privacy Policy","Privacy Policy","","privacy-policy","No","Main","0","","","<p><strong>We are committed to protecting your privacy</strong></p>
<p>We collect the minimum amount of information about you that is  commensurate with providing you with a satisfactory service. This policy  indicates the type of processes that may result in data being collected  about you. Your use of this website gives us the right to collect that  information.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Vacason is committed to keeping the information provided to us by our customers absolutely confidential. We strongly believe in individual\'s right to privacy. We will NEVER sell or disclose any information about our customers to outside parties except as absolutely required to operate the site (Verisign, CC processing, etc.).</p>
<p>Vacason does not authorize the use of \"Spam\" e-mailing and will not release your e-mail address to any other parties.</p>
<p>Vacason will, on occasion (usually twice a month) distribute informational e-mails to our customers announcing update and upcoming events and features. Customers can opt out of this mailing through the customer management screen. Customers who receive the informational e-mail are blind copied so as not to reveal their identity to other members.</p>
<p>VacationHosting and its affiliates utilize SSL security for the transmission of financial transactions and makes every reasonable attempt to protect customer\'s financial data. Customers are urged to protect their login ID and password to prevent unauthorized use of their account. VacationHosting will not be responsible for charges incurred by accounts that have been properly accessed via UserID and appropriate password.</p>
<p>Vacason may use cookies for the convenience of the customer accessing the site. Cookies allow the site to retain data and customer ID without the need for repeated login. Vacason does not utilize or scan cookie information in any way other than to provide this convenience.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Information Collected</strong></p>
<p>We may collect any or all of the information that you give us  depending on the type of transaction you enter into, including your  name, address, telephone number, and email address, together with data  about your use of the website. Other information that may be needed from  time to time to process a request may also be collected as indicated on  the website.</p>
<p><strong>Information Use</strong></p>
<p>We use the information collected primarily to process the task for  which you visited the website. Data collected in the UK is held in  accordance with the Data Protection Act. All reasonable precautions are  taken to prevent unauthorised access to this information. This safeguard  may require you to provide additional forms of identity should you wish  to obtain information about your account details.</p>
<p><strong>Disclosing Information</strong></p>
<p>We do not disclose any personal information obtained about you from  this website to third parties unless you permit us to do so by ticking  the relevant boxes in registration or competition forms. We may also use  the information to keep in contact with you and inform you of  developments associated with us. You will be given the opportunity to  remove yourself from any mailing list or similar device. If at any time  in the future we should wish to disclose information collected on this  website to any third party, it would only be with your knowledge and  consent.&nbsp;</p>
<p>We may from time to time provide information of a general nature to  third parties - for example, the number of individuals visiting our  website or completing a registration form, but we will not use any  information that could identify those individuals.&nbsp;</p>
<p>In addition Vacason may work with third parties for the purpose of  delivering targeted behavioural advertising to the Vacason website.  Through the use of cookies, anonymous information about your use of our  websites and other websites will be used to provide more relevant  adverts about goods and services of interest to you. For more  information on online behavioural advertising and about how to turn this  feature off, please visit vacason.com/opt-out.</p>
<p><strong>Changes to this Policy</strong></p>
<p>Any changes to our Privacy Policy will be placed here and will  supersede this version of our policy. We will take reasonable steps to  draw your attention to any changes in our policy. However, to be on the  safe side, we suggest that you read this document each time you use the  website to ensure that it still meets with your approval.</p>
<p><strong>Contacting Us</strong></p>
<p>If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, or if you want to  know what information we have collected about you, please email us at&nbsp; contact@vacason.com. You can also correct any factual errors in  that information or require us to remove your details form any list  under our control.</p>","Publish","Privacy Policy","en");INSERT INTO fc_cms VALUES("2","Terms of Service","Terms of Service","company","terms-of-service","No","Main","0","","","<p><span>Welcome to Vacason website (the &ldquo;Website&rdquo;, the &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;). (\"Vacason, Vacason.com&rdquo;, &ldquo;Us&rdquo; or &ldquo;We&rdquo;) provides a platform that connects travellers (&ldquo;Guests&rdquo;) looking for accommodations with hosts (&ldquo;Hosts&rdquo;) who want to rent out their available properties (&ldquo;rooms&rdquo;, &ldquo;spaces&rdquo;) in cities across the World.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Agreement:</strong>&nbsp;By registering for or using Vacason.com platform (Website, Apps Services), users agree to follow and be legally bound by the following Terms and Conditions:&nbsp;<br /><br />The Platform comprises of Website and Apps through which Hosts may create listings for accommodations and Guests (Travelers) may book accommodations provided or listed by Hosts.&nbsp;<br />Vacason provides a platform on which Host and Guest can communicate with each other and conclude agreements regarding accommodation. You understand and agree that VacationHosting is not a party to any agreements entered into between Hosts and Guests.&nbsp;<br /><br />You understand that Vacason is not a Real Estate Broker, Real Estate Agent or an Insurance Agent. You understand that Vacason does not examine the accuracy, completeness or legality of offers published on its platform has no control over the conduct of its Hosts or Guests and other users of the platform and disclaims all liability in this regard to the maximum extend permitted by the Law.<br /><br />&nbsp;You understand and agree that Vacason 