</ul>","Publish","Vacason Cancellation Policies","en");INSERT INTO fc_cms VALUES("4","About Vacason","About Vacason","","about","No","Main","0","","","<p class=\"first\"><span>Vacason is an Eco-System of travel and platform that enables people in cities across the world to list unique and amazing&nbsp;accommodations, experiences and adventures, food, events, and travelers worldwide to discover, book and experience&nbsp;such accommodations, adventures, food, events and more for vacation, business, casual and holiday trips.</span><br /><br /><span>At Vacason,&nbsp;Apartments, Houses, Bread &amp; Breakfast, Vacation Rentals, Villas,&nbsp;Cabins, Luxury Properties, Bugalows, Camper/RVs, Castles, Chalets, Coaches, Condos, Earth Houses, Hotels, Huts, Lofts, Tree-houses, Tripi, Lighthouses, &nbsp;Boats, Trains, Planes, Vans, Yurts, Adventures, Events, Food and more can be listed by hosts while enabling travelers (guests) to find and book such listings for vacation, business, casual, holiday or trips and tourism in over 30,000 cities around the World.</span></p>","Publish","Vacason","en");INSERT INTO fc_cms VALUES("5","Press","Press","company","press","Yes","Main","0","","","<p>Vacason Press Releases</p>","Publish","Press","en");INSERT INTO fc_cms VALUES("7","Trust And Safety","Trust And Safety","","trust-and-safety","Yes","Main","0","","","<p><span>Safety of our Hosts and Guests (Travelers) and their accounts on our platform is our number one priority.</span><strong>Safety:<br /></strong><br /><span>Safety of our Hosts and Guests (Travelers) and their accounts on our platform is our number one priority.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><strong>Account Safety:&nbsp;<br /></strong><br /><span>We encourage our users to always use a strong password combination when creating an account on our platform. Passwords can also be changed anytime in user&rsquo;s account. Our platform is secure with latest encryption system (SSL) to ensure safety of our users\' accounts and data.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>For security purpose, we also encourage all users to keep all payment transactions and communication within the Vacason.com platform. Vacason.com can only safeguard payment transactions and communication that occurred within the platform and is not responsible for any payments made offsite.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>Users should always ensure that they working within Vacason.com platform when entering any information on the site. This can be done by looking at the address field of their browsers for&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.vacason.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vacason.com</a>. or&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://vacason.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://vacason.com</a>&nbsp;to ensure they are inside the platform before entering any personal information on the website. Users are also advised not to click any link or download any attachments from unknown sources or websites. VacationHosting.com will never ask any host or traveller to make any payments offsite.&nbsp;</span><br /><span>For further security, users are advised to install Popup blocker and anti-virus software from trust-worthy sources only on their computers or mobile devices to forestall browser hijacks from malicious software on the Internet.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><strong>Property Safety:&nbsp;<br /></strong><br /><span>1. Hosts should ensure that their properties meet housing safety regulations of their respective governments or local authorities.</span><br /><span>2. Hosts should ensure proper ventilation of their properties</span><br /><span>3. Hosts should provide functioning smoke alarm devices and carbon monoxide detectors for their properties.</span><br /><span>4. Hosts should ensure marked fire escape routes within their properties and communicate this information to their guests.</span><br /><span>5. Hosts should ensure that all electrical appliances are properly installed.</span><br /><span>6. Hosts should remove any hazardous material from their properties before the arrival of their guests.</span><br /><span>7. Hosts should make first aid kits available to their guests.</span></p>
